<h2>Payment Confirmed!</h2>
<p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
<p>We are pleased to inform you that your payment for <strong>{{serviceName}}</strong> has been successfully processed.</p>

<div class="details-box">
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Order ID</span>
    <span class="value">{{orderUniqueId}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Service</span>
    <span class="value">{{serviceName}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Amount Paid</span>
    <span class="value">₹{{amount}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Status</span>
    <span class="value" style="color: #22c55e; font-weight: 700;">PAID ✓</span>
  </div>
</div>

<p>You can now proceed with further steps of your service application in your dashboard.</p>

<div class="btn">
  <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td> <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/services" target="_blank">View My Services</a> </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<p>Thank you for choosing Doorstep Filings.</p>
